name: Aarya Srinivasan
title: Co-Founder
description: Hey I'm Aarya! I'm a senior at Archbishop Mitty High School who is a Chair of the Speech and Debate team. One of my accomplishments include being the MLK Invitational Champion, ranked in the top-10 in Policy Debate in California, ranked 4th Congressional Debate in California, and semifinaling at numerous tournaments, such as Berkeley, Stanford, and Glenbrooks. Besides debate, I also love to read books, play the mridangam, and watch sports.
